  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: transaction is not shown in 1:1 chat when trying to send ETH from within the Wallet to a recipient who is in Contacts. But funds amount is decreased\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\ntransaction shoud appear in 1:1 chat when sending ETH from wallet to recipient\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nafter you signed in the transaction it does not appear in 1:1 chat. BUT actual state of wallet is changed: amount is decreased.\r\nSee the moment when this happens: http://recordit.co/ycCdO6AZ3i\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status on two devices: ios and android. Android is primary device.\r\n- Create accounts on both devices.\r\n- Switch to dev mode with ROPSTEN on both devices\r\n- On primary device goto Home -> Plus -> Start new chat. Open QR contact scanner\r\n- On secondary device goto Profile -> Share my contact code\r\n- On primary device scan the contact code of secondary device\r\n- Send a message to secondary device\r\n- Add to contact the person on secondary device\r\n- On primary request /faucet in Status console. Wait until funds come to the wallet.\r\n- On primary device goto Wallet -> LET'S GET SET UP -> Yes\r\n- On primary device goto Send transaction -> Choose recipient -> Contacts and choose a person from secondary device. Specify all funds you have and sign in transaction.\r\n### Additional Information \r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.21 (6121)\r\n* Operating System: primary device Android 8.0 Google Nexus 6P (via Genymotion)\r\nsecondary device real iphone 6s with ios 11.4.1. Status version: 0.9.22 (6164)\r\n\r\nReproduced on: July, 22; 5:52 pm Kiev time\r\n[Link to apk](http://artifacts.status.im:8081/artifactory/nightlies-local/im.status.ethereum-f62e7d-rel.apk)\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote><img src=\"/favicon.ico?v=0.2\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><strong><a href=\"http://recordit.co/ycCdO6AZ3i\">Recordit: Record screencasts fast & free! with GIF Support!</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
